Wenger on being Arsenal manager: &quot;It's a big job. The club has gone through the most difficult period in the last 10 years, building the stadium. I always felt that after 2016 that the club would be in a financial situation where we would compete again.&quot;<br />
<br />
Wenger: &quot;What I could not predict is that clubs would move up another level financially that makes it more difficult now. But I still think Arsenal will come back and compete for the championship.&quot;

